<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" data-theme="light">
<head>
    <title>About Us - FlavorFusion</title>
    <%- include('partials/head') %>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/about.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/footer.css">
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Navigation -->
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main>
        <div class="about-container">
            <div class="about-hero">
                <h1>About FlavorFusion</h1>
                <p>Your ultimate culinary companion for discovering, creating, and sharing delicious recipes</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="about-content">
                <section class="about-section">
                    <div class="about-image">
                        <img src="/images/images.png" alt="Our Mission">
                    </div>
                    <div class="about-text">
                        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                        <p>At FlavorFusion, we're passionate about bringing culinary creativity to your kitchen. Our mission is to inspire home cooks of all skill levels to explore new flavors, techniques, and cuisines.</p>
                        <p>We believe that cooking should be accessible, enjoyable, and rewarding for everyone. That's why we've created a platform that combines recipe discovery, meal planning, and a vibrant community of food enthusiasts.</p>
                    </div>
                </section>
                
                <section class="about-section reverse">
                    <div class="about-image">
                        <img src="/images/image.png" alt="Our Story">
                    </div>
                    <div class="about-text">
                        <h2>Our Story</h2>
                        <p>Founded in 2025, FlavorFusion began as a passion project by a group of friends who shared a love for cooking and technology. What started as a simple recipe-sharing platform quickly evolved into a comprehensive culinary ecosystem.</p>
                        <p>Today, FlavorFusion is a community-driven platform created by food enthusiasts for food enthusiasts. Our team of chefs, nutritionists, and tech experts work together to provide you with the best culinary resources.</p>
                    </div>
                </section>
                
                <section class="about-features">
                    <h2>What We Offer</h2>
                    <div class="features-grid">
                        <div class="feature-card">
                            <i class="fas fa-search"></i>
                            <h3>Recipe Discovery</h3>
                            <p>Explore thousands of recipes from around the world, filtered by cuisine, dietary preferences, or ingredients you have on hand.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature-card">
                            <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt"></i>
                            <h3>Meal Planning</h3>
                            <p>Organize your weekly meals with our intuitive planner, saving you time and reducing food waste.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature-card">
                            <i class="fas fa-shopping-basket"></i>
                            <h3>Shopping Lists</h3>
                            <p>Generate shopping lists from your selected recipes, making grocery shopping efficient and stress-free.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature-card">
                            <i class="fas fa-blog"></i>
                            <h3>Cooking Blog</h3>
                            <p>Learn tips, tricks, and food stories from our community of home cooks and professional chefs.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature-card">
                            <i class="fas fa-user-cog"></i>
                            <h3>Personalized Experience</h3>
                            <p>Save favorites and get recommendations based on your preferences and cooking history.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature-card">
                            <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
                            <h3>Community</h3>
                            <p>Connect with other food enthusiasts, share your creations, and get inspired by others.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>
                
                <section class="about-values">
                    <h2>Our Values</h2>
                    <div class="values-container">
                        <div class="value-item">
                            <h3>Culinary Diversity</h3>
                            <p>We celebrate foods from all cultures and traditions, promoting understanding through shared culinary experiences.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="value-item">
                            <h3>Sustainability</h3>
                            <p>We encourage sustainable cooking practices that are good for both people and the planet.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="value-item">
                            <h3>Accessibility</h3>
                            <p>We believe good food should be accessible to everyone, regardless of skill level or background.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="value-item">
                            <h3>Community</h3>
                            <p>We foster a positive, supportive community where members can learn from and inspire each other.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>
                
                <section class="about-team">
                    <h2>Meet Our Team</h2>
                    <div class="team-grid">
                        <div class="team-member">
                            <img src="/images/muskan.png" alt="Head Chef">
                            <h3>Muskan</h3>
                            <p>Head Chef</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="team-member">
                            <img src="/images/ridhima.png" alt="Nutritionist">
                            <h3>Ridhima Sharma</h3>
                            <p>Nutritionist</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="team-member">
                            <img src="/images/kanav.png" alt="Lead Developer">
                            <h3>Kanav Kumar</h3>
                            <p>Lead Developer</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="team-member">
                            <img src="/images/mitul.png" alt="Community Manager">
                            <h3>Mitul Goyal</h3>
                            <p>Community Manager</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>
                
                <section class="about-join">
                    <h2>Join Our Community</h2>
                    <p>Whether you're a beginner cook or a seasoned chef, FlavorFusion welcomes you to join our growing community. Share your recipes, learn from others, and embark on a flavorful journey with us!</p>
                    <a href="/signup" class="cta-button">Sign Up Now</a>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>

    <!-- Scripts -->
    <script src="/js/theme.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/navigation.js"></script>
</body>
</html> 